# Instructions for OpenHands AI Agent

## Documentation Reference

This project's documentation is maintained exclusively in the `/docs` directory. 
Please refer to these documents for all guidelines, patterns, and requirements:

- `/docs/project-guidelines.md` - Overall project standards
- `/docs/architecture.md` - Architecture and design patterns
- `/docs/code-style-guide.md` - Coding standards and patterns
- `/docs/ai-agent-guide.md` - AI agent development guide
- `/docs/getting-started.md` - Setup and development workflow

## Single Source of Truth

The documentation in the `/docs` directory is the single source of truth for this project.
When resolving issues or implementing features, always follow the guidance in these documents.

## Repository Information

For a basic understanding of the project, this is a CLI tool for managing developer status updates
using git logs and AI. See the documentation for all details about implementation. 